name: User can see titles and pictures on each product inside the off plan page

steps.name: Given Open the main page soft.reelly.io
And Log in to the page.
When Click on “off plan” at the left side menu.
Then Verify the right page opens.
And Verify each product on this page contains a title and picture visible.

fullName: Verify Off plan page: User can see titles and pictures on each product inside the off plan page
